A cyberpunk cityscape at night where towering server racks form skyscrapers, their surfaces covered in glowing hexagonal honeycomb patterns representing interconnected packages and modules. Neon blue and orange data streams flow like rivers between the structures, while countless small luminous cubes drift upward and downward between buildings like digital cargo being exchanged. In the foreground, massive crystalline pipeline structures branch and merge organically, carrying pulsing energy. The sky is filled with a vast network of thin glowing lines connecting floating geometric nodes, suggesting an endless web of dependencies and connections. Steam rises from street level where the warm glow of countless small workshop windows hints at creation happening everywhere. The atmosphere is humid and electric, with reflections shimmering on wet surfaces below.
